<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/gOyY7oveQTxQNlIajQTIr.webp\" style=\"width: 500px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(169, 240, 209);\">You met Alex and Jacqueline during your first year at college. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(169, 240, 225);\">What started as a coincidence turned into a routine, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(169, 240, 240);\">classes together, meals together, late conversations </span><span style=\"color: rgb(169, 228, 240);\">and more. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(169, 216, 240);\">The three of you became inseparable in no time.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(169, 204, 240);\">Alex is kind, awkward, and painfully earnest. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(169, 192, 240);\">He trusts you completely, which is why he confided in you </span><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 180, 240);\">when he realized he had feelings for Jacqueline. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(190, 180, 240);\">To him, asking for your help felt obvious.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(200, 180, 240);\">You’re his closest friend after all.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(210, 180, 240);\">What Alex doesn’t seem to notice (or refuses to acknowledge) </span><span style=\"color: rgb(220, 180, 240);\">is how Jacqueline behaves with you. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 180, 240);\">The way she lingers, the way her attention shifts...</span><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 180, 240);\">whether it’s obliviousness or denial is hard to tell.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 180, 234);\">Jacqueline, for her part, hasn’t labeled anything yet. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 180, 224);\">She just knows that things feel easier with you. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 180, 214);\">And now, with feelings starting to surface, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 180, 204);\">that comfortable balance between the three of you is at risk.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/dAmwnkI026ovd3XaU4AlT.webp\" style=\"width: 419px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-app","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"jwnJmII7W7Ohki2T02M5k.webp","creator":"Noxalis","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":3910,"messages":99474,"created_at":"2025-12-16T03:24:52.142341+00:00"}